    {
      "id": "33",
      "name": "Gallery",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "id": "gallery_character77898",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/05/14/f5e398fb5e6e2ab0c6db9bcabf6f5646_1097173885447251291.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>The enigmatic \"symphony\" seems to be from a now-destroyed civilization.<br>You can use its power to unleash <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">two types of soundwaves</span>.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/3"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character92794",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/05/14/00b4e46cc5a64c4ce92801478d8cc46c_4501794631655836797.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Use the power of the \"Symphony\" to resonate with entities that react to the power of music.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">Press to activate a Pause Soundwave</span> and cause specific objects in the area to stop moving. Continuously <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">Hold to activate a Play Soundwave</span>, which will cause specific objects in the area to start moving or reactivate entities affected by a<span style=\"color: #FFE14B\"> Pause Soundwave</span>.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/3"
              },
              {
                "id": "gallery_character68584",
                "img": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/05/14/9294313b859193c66723732a6486b8a5_8619877785701259726.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Special musical notes</span> float above objects that can be influenced by the power of the \"symphony.\" When they resonate with specific soundwaves, the notes above them will also change.<br>Not all objects that can be influenced by music can resonate with different soundwaves. Most of them can only interact with a specific soundwave.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/3"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
